    "panels": [
      {
        "text": "### Creative Coding\n\nThis is Roxanne",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/6f1a4dd47abe027f95a96f189703b87a-roxanne1.png",
        "key": "test-music-lab-loops-sythesize-project-panels-25e9b5d9-07a8-4064-9fb2-75fa8d2262e3",
        "layout": "text-top-right"
      },
      {
        "text": "### Creative Coding\n\nShe's an Artist, Creator, and Coder\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/31de70a2eb96f9e6de2fd7926fef44af-roxanne2.png",
        "key": "test-music-lab-loops-sythesize-project-panels-0b5eb9b2-25d6-472d-9f49-a3c50f1a0b1a",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true,
        "layout": "text-bottom-right"
      },
      {
        "text": "### Creative Coding\n\nRoxanne performs music using Code",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/daa047d1614da0edd689079fc5119477-roxanne3.png",
        "key": "test-music-lab-loops-sythesize-project-panels-d145b67c-8a93-4174-92c5-f1215a77cb2b",
        "layout": "text-bottom-right",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "### Creative Coding\n\nShe edits the code live in front of an audience\n\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/aff8ceef94afd6c4e912625315bdba2a-roxanne4.png",
        "key": "test-music-lab-loops-sythesize-project-panels-fb2f98b1-b7e5-4636-a99b-1450c3ccae64",
        "layout": "text-bottom-right",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "\"As I change the code, the music changes with it\"",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/10195782b8a92beb3b053b2b8947a4ef-roxanne5.png",
        "key": "test-music-lab-loops-sythesize-project-panels-0e55f57b-3524-4334-b2fc-6cc466c0e847",
        "layout": "text-bottom-center",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true,
        "typing": true
      },
      {
        "text": "\"I'm just giving instructions on how and when to make sound\"",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/732afda4c264bf088873fd6daaaa23ef-roxanne6.png",
        "key": "test-music-lab-loops-sythesize-project-panels-177676fb-e459-49fb-9aa9-4dbc047d67f3",
        "layout": "text-bottom-center",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true,
        "typing": true
      },
      {
        "text": "### Creative Coding\n\nIn this lesson, we're going to try Live Coding in Music Lab!",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/66baa69141692193dc2f847639394a24-live-loop-2.gif",
        "key": "test-music-lab-loops-sythesize-project-panels-98fbe714-ece3-4234-8117-2262cc925466",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "\"The most rewarding part about being a creative programmer is using programming to create something I feel really passionate about\"",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/746ff340c500481898ab66d51cf411e8-roxanne8.png",
        "key": "test-music-lab-loops-sythesize-project-panels-0a63e0c0-3e78-48a6-8222-48a8750ff79a",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true,
        "typing": true,
        "layout": "text-bottom-center"
      },
      {
        "text": "\"Passion is an important part of learning to code and finding your style and finding your way\"",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/7d2963acbd87ff78babeb70c20178419-roxanne7.png",
        "key": "test-music-lab-loops-sythesize-project-panels-6a94c904-ca6c-4f46-a405-97c26f98e368",
        "typing": true,
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true,
        "layout": "text-bottom-center"
      }
    ],
    "name_suffix": "_v2"
  },
